{"title":"Horizon基础介绍与安装使用","slug":"虚拟云容/虚拟化/VMware/Horizon/Horizon基础介绍与安装使用","date":"2019-06-16T02:36:30.000Z","updated":"2023-01-31T02:29:10.471Z","url":"2019/6-16-493.html","path":"api/articles/2019/6-16-493.html.json","covers":["https://img.weiyigeek.top/2021/5/20210718155632.png","https://img.weiyigeek.top/2021/5/20210718155958.png"],"content":"<p>[TOC]</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>官方介绍: <a href=\"https://www.vmware.com/cn/products/horizon.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.vmware.com/cn/products/horizon.html</a></p>\n<p><strong>Q: 什么是 VMware Horizon ?</strong><br>A: VMware Horizon 是一个现代平台，可跨混合云高效、安全地交付虚拟桌面和应用(<code>虚拟桌面基础架构 (VDI) 软件</code>)，从而实现最佳的终端用户数字化工作空间体验, 意味着可以将桌面和应用管理简化和自动化，并增强安全性。</p>\n<p><strong>Q: 什么是 VMware Horizon Client？</strong><br>A: VMware Horizon Client 是一款软件，让您能够将 VMware Horizon 虚拟桌面连接到所选设备，从而随时随地进行移动访问。Client 适用于 Windows、Mac、iOS、Linux、Chrome 和 Android.<br>下载地址: <a href=\"https://my.vmware.com/en/web/vmware/downloads/info/slug/desktop_end_user_computing/vmware_horizon_clients/horizon_8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://my.vmware.com/en/web/vmware/downloads/info/slug/desktop_end_user_computing/vmware_horizon_clients/horizon_8</a></p>\n<p>VMware Horizon 的工作原理是什么？</p>\n<p>VMware Horizon 在数据中心或云环境中运行远程桌面和应用，并将它们作为代管服务提供给员工</p>\n<p><em>Q: VMware Horizon 是 VPN 吗？</em></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A: VMware Horizon 不是虚拟专用网络 (VPN)。它使用 Unified Access Gateway (UAG) 来提供对 Horizon 的安全远程访问。它确实支持通过 VPN 远程访问桌面和应用，但是通常不需要将 VPN 与 UAG 一起使用。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"0x0n-出坑入坑\"><a href=\"#0x0n-出坑入坑\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"0x0n 出坑入坑\"></a>0x0n 出坑入坑</h2><h3 id=\"问题1-vmware-horizon-client-安装一半自动取消然后安装失败。\"><a href=\"#问题1-vmware-horizon-client-安装一半自动取消然后安装失败。\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题1.vmware horizon client 安装一半自动取消然后安装失败。\"></a>问题1.vmware horizon client 安装一半自动取消然后安装失败。</h3><p><strong>解决办法:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>方式1.安装时选择自定义安装并把不需要的东西勾掉然后再安装。<figure class=\"image-box\">\n                <img src=\"https://img.weiyigeek.top/2021/5/20210718155632.png\" alt=\"WeiyiGeek.VMWareInstall\" title=\"\" class=\"\">\n                <p>WeiyiGeek.VMWareInstall</p>\n            </figure></li>\n<li>方式2.验证<code>C:\\Windows\\System32\\drivers\\etc\\hosts</code>文件是否存在并且权限不能为只读<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">PS C:\\Users\\WeiyiGeek&gt; Get-Item -path <span class=\"string\">\"C:\\Windows\\System32\\drivers\\etc\\hosts\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">#     目录: C:\\Windows\\System32\\drivers\\etc</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\"># Mode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\"># ----                 -------------         ------ ----</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\"># -a----         2021/7/16     11:32           2455 hosts</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">PS C:\\Users\\WeiyiGeek&gt; start C:\\Windows\\System32\\drivers\\etc\\</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"image-box\">\n                <img src=\"https://img.weiyigeek.top/2021/5/20210718155958.png\" alt=\"WeiyiGeek.主机hosts文件权限\" title=\"\" class=\"\">\n                <p>WeiyiGeek.主机hosts文件权限</p>\n            </figure></li>\n</ul>\n","comments":true,"excerpt":"[TOC]","categories":[{"name":"VMware","path":"api/categories/VMware.json"},{"name":"virtualization","path":"api/categories/virtualization.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"vCenter","path":"api/tags/vCenter.json"}]}